---
import PageLayout from '@layouts/PageLayout.astro';

const pageTitle = "Chengdu's Rise in Small-Batch Custom Women's Shoes: A Deep Dive into China's Footwear Industry Geographic Distribution";
const description = "Analysis of China's footwear industry regional distribution in 2025, with focus on Chengdu's transformation from mass production to small-batch custom manufacturing.";
const publishedTime = "2026-05-11";
const authors = ["ChinaShoe Editorial Team"];
const tags = ["industry analysis", "China footwear", "Chengdu", "small-batch manufacturing", "产业集群"];

const breadcrumbs = [
  { name: 'Home', url: '/' },
  { name: 'News', url: '/news/' },
  { name: 'Chengdu Small-Batch Custom Shoes', url: '/news/chengdu-small-batch-custom-women-shoes/' },
];
---

<PageLayout
  title={pageTitle}
  description={description}
  breadcrumbs={breadcrumbs}
  publishedTime={publishedTime}
  authors={authors}
  tags={tags}
>
  <div class="mb-8">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
      <span class="badge-primary">Industry Analysis</span>
      <span class="text-sm text-neutral-500">May 11, 2026</span>
    </div>
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">
      China's Footwear Industry Geographic Distribution: Deep Analysis
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-neutral-600">
      Chengdu's Rise in Small-Batch Custom Women's Shoes
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Featured Image -->
  <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden mb-8">
    <img
      src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1441986300917-64674bd700d4?w=1200&h=400&fit=crop"
      alt="China Footwear Manufacturing - Industrial Cluster Distribution"
      class="w-full h-64 md:h-80 object-cover"
    />
  </div>

  <!-- Key Statistics -->
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-12">
    <div class="card p-6">
      <p class="text-lg text-blue-700 font-medium mb-2">2025 China Footwear Industry Total Output</p>
      <p class="text-5xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-2">980<span class="text-2xl ml-2">Billion CNY</span></p>
      <p class="text-base text-gray-500">Year-over-year growth: <span class="font-semibold text-blue-700">8.2%</span></p>
    </div>
    <div class="card p-6">
      <p class="text-lg text-green-700 font-medium mb-2">2025 China Footwear Total Production</p>
      <p class="text-5xl font-bold text-green-900 mb-2">13<span class="text-2xl ml-2">Billion Pairs</span></p>
      <p class="text-base text-gray-500">Accounting for over <span class="font-semibold text-green-700">60%</span> of global production</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Article Content -->
  <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">China's Footwear Industry Cluster Distribution</h2>

    <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-4">
      China's footwear industry exhibits a distinct geographic concentration pattern, with five major production clusters emerging across different provinces. Each cluster has developed specialized capabilities based on local industrial heritage, workforce expertise, and supply chain ecosystems.
    </p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-5 gap-4 mb-8">
      <div class="text-center p-4 bg-blue-50 rounded-lg">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-3 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z"/>
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-800">Guangdong</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Design & R&D<br>Export Trade</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center p-4 bg-green-50 rounded-lg">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-3 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z"/>
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-800">Fujian</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Sports Shoes<br>Industrial Cluster</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center p-4 bg-amber-50 rounded-lg">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-3 bg-amber-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-amber-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z"/>
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-800">Zhejiang</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Leather Shoes<br>Wenzhou Model</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center p-4 bg-rose-50 rounded-lg">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-3 bg-rose-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-rose-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z"/>
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-800">Jiangsu</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Industry Transfer<br>Supporting Industries</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center p-4 bg-purple-50 rounded-lg">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-3 bg-purple-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z"/>
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-800">Sichuan</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Women's Leather Shoes<br>Small-Batch Custom</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="text-gray-600 italic text-center mb-8">
      The "Three States One Capital" Geographic Pattern: Guangzhou, Wenzhou, Quanzhou, and Chengdu
    </p>

    <!-- Regional Production Comparison -->
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">2025 Major Production Regions Output Comparison</h2>

    <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-8">
      <table class="w-full">
        <thead>
          <tr class="border-b-2 border-neutral-200">
            <th class="text-left py-3 px-4 font-bold text-neutral-700">Province</th>
            <th class="text-left py-3 px-4 font-bold text-neutral-700">Output (Billion CNY)</th>
            <th class="text-left py-3 px-4 font-bold text-neutral-700">Percentage</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr class="border-b border-neutral-100">
            <td class="py-3 px-4 font-medium">Fujian</td>
            <td class="py-3 px-4">220</td>
            <td class="py-3 px-4">24.4%</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-b border-neutral-100">
            <td class="py-3 px-4 font-medium">Guangdong</td>
            <td class="py-3 px-4">190</td>
            <td class="py-3 px-4">21.1%</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-b border-neutral-100">
            <td class="py-3 px-4 font-medium">Zhejiang</td>
            <td class="py-3 px-4">160</td>
            <td class="py-3 px-4">17.8%</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-b border-neutral-100">
            <td class="py-3 px-4 font-medium">Sichuan</td>
            <td class="py-3 px-4">35</td>
            <td class="py-3 px-4">3.9%</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-b border-neutral-100">
            <td class="py-3 px-4 font-medium">Henan</td>
            <td class="py-3 px-4">30</td>
            <td class="py-3 px-4">3.3%</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-b border-neutral-100">
            <td class="py-3 px-4 font-medium">Anhui</td>
            <td class="py-3 px-4">28</td>
            <td class="py-3 px-4">3.1%</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>

    <!-- Chengdu Focus Section -->
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">Chengdu Women's Shoe Industry Transformation</h2>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-8">
      <div>
        <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-6">
          While Chengdu's women's shoe industry experienced a dramatic adjustment from 600 million pairs to 200 million pairs annually, it has discovered new growth momentum in the small-batch custom segment—a niche market that plays to the region's traditional strengths.
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-600 mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
            </svg>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800">Deep Historical Heritage</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Over 1,800 years of shoemaking history with exquisite handcraftsmanship traditions</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-600 mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
            </svg>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800">Flexible Production Capability</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Orders ranging from a few pairs to 2,000 pairs with rapid response times</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-600 mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
            </svg>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800">Complete Industrial Chain</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Full ecosystem from leather supply, shoe materials, to finished product manufacturing</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-purple-50 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-purple-900 mb-4">Chengdu Women's Shoe Industry Data</h3>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="text-center">
            <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-purple-700">200M</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Annual Output</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-purple-700">95%</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Women's Shoes Share</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-purple-700">1/3</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">National Women's Shoe Exports</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-purple-700">4B+</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Douyin E-commerce GMV (CNY)</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Image: Chengdu Workshop -->
    <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden mb-8">
      <img
        src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1558618666-fcd25c85cd64?w=1200&h=300&fit=crop"
        alt="Chengdu Small-Batch Shoe Manufacturing Workshop"
        class="w-full h-48 md:h-64 object-cover"
      />
    </div>

    <!-- Four Major Clusters Comparison -->
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">Comparison of Four Major Footwear Industrial Clusters</h2>

    <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-8">
      <table class="w-full">
        <thead>
          <tr class="border-b-2 border-green-100">
            <th class="pb-3 font-bold text-neutral-700">City/Region</th>
            <th class="pb-3 font-bold text-neutral-700">Number of Enterprises</th>
            <th class="pb-3 font-bold text-neutral-700">Annual Output</th>
            <th class="pb-3 font-bold text-neutral-700">Main Products</th>
            <th class="pb-3 font-bold text-neutral-700">Core Advantages</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr class="border-b border-gray-100">
            <td class="py-4 font-medium">Dongguan</td>
            <td class="py-4">5,200+</td>
            <td class="py-4">126 million pairs</td>
            <td class="py-4">Sports shoes, Casual shoes</td>
            <td class="py-4">Large-scale production, OEM</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-b border-gray-100">
            <td class="py-4 font-medium">Wenzhou Lucheng</td>
            <td class="py-4">2,000+</td>
            <td class="py-4">600 million pairs</td>
            <td class="py-4">Women's shoes as main focus</td>
            <td class="py-4">Leather shoe manufacturing, Branding</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-b border-gray-100">
            <td class="py-4 font-medium">Jinjiang Chendai</td>
            <td class="py-4">7,000+</td>
            <td class="py-4">1 billion pairs</td>
            <td class="py-4">Sports shoes</td>
            <td class="py-4">Brand operations, Full industry chain</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="py-4 font-medium">Chengdu</td>
            <td class="py-4">&lt;500</td>
            <td class="py-4">200 million pairs</td>
            <td class="py-4">Women's shoes 95%</td>
            <td class="py-4">Handcraft, Small-batch custom</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>

    <!-- Chengdu Development Timeline Image -->
    <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden mb-8">
      <img
        src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1560472354-b33ff0c44a43?w=1200&h=300&fit=crop"
        alt="Chengdu Footwear Industry Historical Evolution"
        class="w-full h-48 md:h-64 object-cover"
      />
    </div>

    <!-- Chengdu Industry Development History -->
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">Chengdu Women's Shoe Industry Development Timeline</h2>

    <div class="bg-rose-50 rounded-xl p-6 mb-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-6 gap-4 text-center">
        <div>
          <p class="text-xl font-bold text-rose-700">2000</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">200M pairs</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">50B CNY output</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-xl font-bold text-rose-700">2005</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">400M pairs</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">150B CNY output</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-xl font-bold text-rose-700">2010</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">600M pairs (peak)</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">250B CNY output</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-xl font-bold text-rose-700">2015</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">400M pairs</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">200B CNY output</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-xl font-bold text-rose-700">2020</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">250M pairs</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">300B CNY output</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-xl font-bold text-rose-700">2025</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">200M pairs</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">350B CNY output</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Future Outlook -->
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">Future Outlook for Chengdu Small-Batch Custom Women's Shoes</h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-8">
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-800 mb-4 flex items-center">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"/>
          </svg>
          Development Opportunities
        </h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-600 mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
            </svg>
            <span>Growth in personalized demands driven by consumption upgrades</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-600 mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
            </svg>
            <span>Rapid development of cross-border e-commerce provides new channels</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-600 mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
            </svg>
            <span>Live-streaming e-commerce innovates "factory-to-consumer" model</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-600 mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
            </svg>
            <span>Policy environment continues to improve providing support</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-800 mb-4 flex items-center">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2"/>
          </svg>
          Development Recommendations
        </h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-600 mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
            </svg>
            <span>Adhere to "small but beautiful" differentiated positioning</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-600 mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
            </svg>
            <span>Strengthen design innovation capabilities, build "Chengdu Design" brand</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-600 mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
            </svg>
            <span>Build industrial ecosystem, form one-stop service cluster</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-600 mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
            </svg>
            <span>Promote digital transformation, improve custom efficiency</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Final Image: Women Shoes Display -->
    <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden mb-8">
      <img
        src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1543163521-1bf539c55dd2?w=1200&h=300&fit=crop"
        alt="Women's Leather Shoes Custom Manufacturing Display"
        class="w-full h-48 md:h-64 object-cover"
      />
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">Conclusion</h2>

    <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-4">
      China's footwear industry demonstrates remarkable regional specialization, with each cluster leveraging its unique strengths. Chengdu's transformation from mass production to high-value small-batch custom manufacturing exemplifies how traditional industrial clusters can adapt to changing market conditions.
    </p>

    <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-4">
      For B2B buyers seeking women's leather shoes with flexible MOQs and custom capabilities, Chengdu offers a compelling combination of craftsmanship tradition, responsive production, and competitive pricing. The region's focus on small-batch orders of 2-2000 pairs makes it ideal for brands testing new designs or serving specialty market segments.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Related Articles -->
  <div class="border-t border-neutral-200 pt-8">
    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-4">Related Articles</h3>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
